  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.5.9">
<l>collīreṉ ṉammāṉai yeṉṉāvi yāvitaṉai</l>
<l>yellaiyil cīreṉ karumāṇik kaccuṭarai</l>
<l>nalla vamutam peṟarkkariya vīṭumā</l>
<l>yalli malarvirai yottā ṉāṇallaṉ peṇṇallaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Speak: my lord, the soul of my soul,</l>
<l>my black ruby effulgence of boundless excellence,</l>
<l>being good ambrosia and liberation difficult to obtain,</l> 
<l>he equals the scent of the water-lily blossom, he is not man, he is not woman.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
